## EMERGENCY PROTOCOL

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Normal: Daily Posting
    Normal --> BufferLow: Buffer < 3 days
    BufferLow --> Emergency: Buffer = 0 days
    
    state Emergency {
        [*] --> Simplify: Simplify Content
        Simplify --> Reuse: Reuse Best Content
        Reuse --> Communicate: Tell Audience
        Communicate --> Rebuild: Rebuild Buffer
        Rebuild --> [*]
    }
    
    Emergency --> Normal: Buffer > 7 days
    BufferLow --> Normal: Buffer > 7 days
```

